Design Consultant<br>
You - are passionate about helping others<br>
You - get excited when you see other people's enthusiasm about your suggestions<br>
You - like seeing and working with a client from the greeting to the finished product<br>
You - have a talent for asking the right questions and listening<br>
You - like to look at creative sites like Pinterest and Houzz<br>
You - want to have the freedom to create your own business and destiny<br>
You - are a team player and build relationships that last<br>
Job Description<br>
If you are looking for a career, not a job and have a passion for people with a flair for design, you may be the candidate we are looking for. At Direct Carpet One Floor &amp; Home you earn customers' trust as the design expert by educating and partnering with them. Your expertise and extensive knowledge of the flooring industry coupled with your customer service brilliance will guarantee that you are the go to person when someone thinks of flooring. If you are a self-motivated and detail orientated individual, we will provide the tools and training you need to achieve outstanding success.  <br>
Job Requirements<br>
•	Customer service, closing sales, prospecting, product knowledge, measuring, scheduling installations, building client relationships. <br>
•	A passion for design and decorating<br>
•	Access to reliable transportation in order to get to work and visit customers' homes<br>
•	Strong knowledge of Microsoft Office programs<br>
•	Ability to work in a team environment<br>
•	Organized and capable of juggling multiple (and sometimes competing) deadlines and deliverables<br>
<br>
We offer the following opportunities and benefits:<br>
•	90 day training salary then transitioning to salary plus commission<br>
•	Health insurance<br>
•	Vacation <br>
•	Discounts on products and services<br>
<br>
Our Proud Heritage:<br>
Direct Carpet One Floor &amp; Home has long been regarded as the premier flooring store in Scottsdale, AZ and surrounding communities.  Locally owned and operated for more than 35 years, we are known for our superior customer service, and professional staff.  <br>
We believe in creating a family friendly work environment, where each person is an integral member of the team, yet responsible for his or her own results and earning potential.  We are proud of our heritage and would like to find an individual who will excel and prosper in a fast paced retail environment, becoming a valued member of our team.<br>
How to Apply:<br>
Please provide the following:<br>
•	Please use the response option in this job board.<br>
•	An up-to-date resume outlining your experience for the position<br>
•	A cover letter is always appreciated<br>
•	Salary history and/or requirements<br>
<br>
We kindly ask for no emails or phone calls be sent to our store, as a means to further your application process.  Please do not personally deliver resumes to the store. These efforts will not enhance your opportunity for consideration, and we are not equipped to respond to these requests.  We thank you kindly in advance for your adherence to this request. <br>
Candidates who meet our selection criteria will be contacted by e-mail or phone for the next step in our hiring process, and in certain instances may be asked to take an online assessment.<br>
Thank you for your interest in our position.  We appreciate the time you have taken to apply with us.<br>
<br>
Direct Carpet One Floor &amp; Home is an Equal Opportunity Employer<br>
    </section>

